      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison of predicted vs. measured hemolysis index at all five operating points with reported error metrics.",
      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) values were compared to FDA experimental measurements at all five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute percentage error was 12.3% across operating points, within the acceptable range for MRL 2. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion satisfied for the device under assessment."
